# Auto-Generated File — Do Not Edit

This file is produced by `schemagen` from `dubhe.config.ts`.
**Any manual changes will be overwritten** the next time schemagen runs.

## How to Make Changes

| What you want to change | What to edit |
|-------------------------|-------------|
| Add / rename / remove an error | `errors` section in `dubhe.config.ts` |
| Add / change a resource or its fields | `resources` section in `dubhe.config.ts` |
| Add a new enum type | `enums` section in `dubhe.config.ts` |

After editing the config, regenerate:
```sh
# Run in framework/ and e2e/ (keep both in sync)
node node_modules/@0xobelisk/sui-cli/dist/dubhe.js schemagen
```

## Files Managed by Schemagen
- `codegen/errors.move`
- `codegen/genesis.move`
- `codegen/dapp_key.move`
- `codegen/init_test.move`
- `codegen/resources/*.move`

Hand-written logic belongs in `systems/`, `core/`, or `utils/`.
